<h1 class="hero-h">Claude for Real Estate Agents: <em>what actually works in 2026.</em></h1>
<p class="hero-sub">Anthropic's Claude is the strongest LLM for reasoning, writing, and long-context work. For real estate agents, it's most valuable for listing descriptions, buyer/seller communications, market reports, and social content. This is the practical playbook with specific use cases, prompts that work, and what to avoid.</p>
<div class="verdict"><div class="verdict-l">The short version</div><p class="verdict-p">Real estate agents should use Claude for listing descriptions, buyer/seller communications, market reports, and social content. Plus daily-driver use cases: client follow-up sequences and comparative market analysis. Cost: $20 (Pro) or $30/seat (Team). Pair with workflow-specific tools for production deployment. Most agents see 3-5x productivity lift on the right tasks.</p></div>
</div></div>

